<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-d19c9277c44872f17ce7d27b6ff8a0d2e34ae850"><a href="#bottom"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-bottom.png" alt="[BOTTOM]" height="10" width="14"></a><a href="#top"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-top.png" alt="[TOP]" height="10" width="14"></a>The Spear of Melkor (4d6) (+12,+24)</h2>
<em>The mighty spear used once by Melkor to slay the trees of Valinor.</em> <p>
It decreases your wisdom and stealth by 4. It poisons your foes. It provides resistance to light, dark, blindness, confusion and nether.  It allows you to sense the presence of good beings. It drains mana and life. It is heavily cursed. It carries an ancient foul curse. 
</p>
